#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2068 l10n/source/edge.xml:2573
msgid "K8s upgrade - SUC plan deployment"
msgstr "K8sアップグレード - SUC Planのデプロイメント"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2074
msgid ""
"As mentioned in <xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-overview\"/"
">, Kubernetes upgrades are done by shipping <literal>SUC plans</literal> to "
"the desired cluster through one of the following ways:"
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-overview\"/>で説明したよう"
"に、Kubernetesアップグレードは、次のいずれかの方法を使用して<literal>SUC "
"Plan</literal>を目的のクラスタに配布することで実行されます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2075
msgid ""
"Fleet GitRepo resource (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-"
"plan-deployment-gitrepo\"/>)"
msgstr ""
"Fleet GitRepoリソース(<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-plan-"
"deployment-gitrepo\"/>)"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2076
msgid ""
"Fleet Bundle resource (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-"
"plan-deployment-bundle\"/>)"
msgstr ""
"Fleetバンドルリソース(<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-plan-"
"deployment-bundle\"/>)"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2078
msgid ""
"For use-cases where you wish to deploy the <literal>K8s SUC plans</literal> "
"from a third-party GitOps tool, refer to <xref linkend=\"management-day2-"
"fleet-k8s-upgrade-plan-deployment-third-party\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<literal>K8s SUC Plan</literal>をサードパーティのGitOpsツールからデプロイする"
"ユースケースの場合は、<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-plan-"
"deployment-third-party\"/>を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2080 l10n/source/edge.xml:2585
msgid ""
"A <emphasis role=\"strong\">GitRepo</emphasis> resource, that ships the "
"needed <literal>K8s SUC plans</literal>, can be deployed in one of the "
"following ways:"
msgstr ""
"必要な<literal>K8s SUC Plan</literal>を配布する、<emphasis role=\"strong\">"
"GitRepo</emphasis>リソースは、次の方法のいずれかでデプロイできます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2081
msgid ""
"Through the <literal>Rancher UI</literal> - <xref linkend=\"management-day2-"
"fleet-k8s-upgrade-plan-deployment-gitrepo-rancher\"/> (when "
"<literal>Rancher</literal> is available)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Rancher UI</literal> - <xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-"
"upgrade-plan-deployment-gitrepo-rancher\"/>を通じて(<literal>Rancher</"
"literal>が利用可能な場合)。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2082
msgid ""
"By manually deploying (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-"
"plan-deployment-gitrepo-manual\"/>) the resource to your <literal>management "
"cluster</literal>."
msgstr ""
"リソースを<literal>管理クラスタ</literal>に手動でデプロイする(<xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade-plan-deployment-gitrepo-"
