"This will load all images from the <literal>edge-images.tar.gz</literal>, "
"retag and push them to the registry specified under the <literal>--registry</"
"literal> option."
msgstr ""
"これにより、<literal>edge-images.tar.gz</literal>からすべてのイメージがロード"
"され、再タグ付けされて、それらを<literal>--registry</literal>オプションで指定"
"されているレジストリにプッシュします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2197 l10n/source/edge.xml:2694
msgid "Load the Edge OCI chart images to your air-gapped machine"
msgstr "Edge OCIチャートイメージのエアギャップマシンへのロード"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2200 l10n/source/edge.xml:2697
msgid "Make <literal>edge-load-oci-artefacts.sh</literal> executable:"
msgstr "<literal>edge-load-oci-artefacts.sh</literal>を実行可能にします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2201 l10n/source/edge.xml:2698
msgid "Untar the copied <literal>oci-artefacts.tar.gz</literal> archive:"
msgstr "コピーした<literal>oci-artefacts.tar.gz</literal>アーカイブをuntarします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2202 l10n/source/edge.xml:2699
msgid ""
"This will produce a directory with the naming template <literal>edge-release-"
"oci-tgz-&lt;date&gt;</literal>"
msgstr ""
"命名テンプレート<literal>edge-release-oci-tgz-&lt;date&gt;</literal>を含む"
"ディレクトリが生成されます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2203 l10n/source/edge.xml:2700
msgid ""
"Pass this directory to the <literal>edge-load-oci-artefacts.sh</literal> "
"script to load the Edge OCI chart images to your private registry:"
msgstr ""
"このディレクトリを<literal>edge-load-oci-artefacts.sh</literal>スクリプトに渡"
"し、Edge OCIチャートイメージをプライベートレジストリにロードします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2204 l10n/source/edge.xml:2701
msgid ""
"This script assumes the <literal>helm</literal> CLI has been pre-installed "
"on your environment. For Helm installation instructions, see <link "
"xl:href=\"https://helm.sh/docs/intro/install/\">Installing Helm</link>."
msgstr ""
"このスクリプトは、<literal>Helm</literal> CLIが環境にプリインストールされてい"
"ることを想定しています。Helmのインストール手順については、「<link "
"xl:href=\"https://helm.sh/docs/intro/install/\">Installing Helm (Helmの"
"インストール)</link>」を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2205 l10n/source/edge.xml:2702
msgid "Configure your private registry in your Kubernetes distribution"
msgstr "Kubernetesディストリビューションでプライベートレジストリを設定する"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2206 l10n/source/edge.xml:2703
msgid ""
"For RKE2, see <link xl:href=\"https://docs.rke2.io/install/"
"private_registry\">Private Registry Configuration</link>"
msgstr ""
"RKE2の場合は、「<link xl:href=\"https://docs.rke2.io/install/"
"private_registry\">Private Registry Configuration (プライベートレジストリの設"
"定)</link>」を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2207 l10n/source/edge.xml:2704
msgid ""
"For K3s, see <link xl:href=\"https://docs.k3s.io/installation/private-"
"registry\">Private Registry Configuration</link>"
msgstr ""
"K3sの場合は、「<link xl:href=\"https://docs.k3s.io/installation/private-"
"registry\">Private Registry Configuration (プライベートレジストリの設定)</"
"link>」を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2208 l10n/source/edge.xml:2705
msgid "Upgrade procedure"
msgstr "アップグレード手順"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2209 l10n/source/edge.xml:2706
msgid "This section focuses on the following Helm upgrade procedure use-cases:"
msgstr ""
"このセクションでは、Helmアップグレード手順の次のユースケースを中心に説明しま"
"す。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2210
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-cluster\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-cluster\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2211
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-fleet-managed-"
"chart\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-fleet-managed-"
"chart\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2212
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-"
"chart\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-"
"chart\"/>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2213
msgid ""
"Manually deployed Helm charts cannot be reliably upgraded. We suggest to "
"redeploy the Helm chart using the <xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-"
"upgrade-procedure-new-cluster\"/> method."
msgstr ""
"手動でデプロイしたHelmチャートを確実にアップグレードすることはできません"
"。<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-"
"cluster\"/>で説明する方法を使用してHelmチャートを再デプロイすることをお勧めし"
"ます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2214 l10n/source/edge.xml:2711
msgid ""
"I have a new cluster and would like to deploy and manage an Edge Helm chart"
msgstr "新しいクラスタがあり、Edge Helmチャートをデプロイして管理したい"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2215 l10n/source/edge.xml:2712
msgid "This section covers how to:"
msgstr "このセクションでは、以下の実行方法について説明します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2216
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-cluster-"
"prepare\"/>."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-cluster-"
"prepare\"/>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2217
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-cluster-"
"deploy\"/>."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-cluster-"
"deploy\"/>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2218
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-cluster-"
"manage\"/>."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-cluster-"
"manage\"/>."

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2219 l10n/source/edge.xml:2716
msgid "Prepare the fleet resources for your chart"
msgstr "チャートのFleetリソースの準備"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2220 l10n/source/edge.xml:2717
msgid ""
"Acquire the chart’s Fleet resources from the Edge <link xl:href=\"https://"
"github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/releases\">release</link> tag that you "
"wish to use."
msgstr ""
"チャートのFleetリソースを、使用するEdge<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/"
"suse-edge/fleet-examples/releases\">リリース</link>タグから取得します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2221 l10n/source/edge.xml:2718
msgid ""
"Navigate to the Helm chart fleet (<literal>fleets/day2/chart-templates/"
"&lt;chart&gt;</literal>)"
msgstr ""
"HelmチャートのFleet (<literal>fleets/day2/chart-templates/&lt;chart&gt;</"
"literal>)に移動します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2222 l10n/source/edge.xml:2719
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">If you intend to use a GitOps workflow</emphasis>, "
"copy the chart Fleet directory to the Git repository from where you will do "
"GitOps."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">GitOpsワークフローを使用する場合は</emphasis>、"
"チャートFleetディレクトリをGitOpsを実行するGitリポジトリにコピーします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2223 l10n/source/edge.xml:2720
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Optionally</emphasis>, if the Helm chart requires "
"configurations to its <emphasis role=\"strong\">values</emphasis>, edit the "
"<literal>.helm.values</literal> configuration inside the "
"<literal>fleet.yaml</literal> file of the copied directory."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">(任意)</emphasis> Helmチャートで<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">値</emphasis>を設定する必要がある場合は、コピーした"
"ディレクトリの<literal>fleet.yaml</literal>ファイルに含まれる設定<literal>"
".helm.values</literal>を編集します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2224 l10n/source/edge.xml:2721
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Optionally</emphasis>, there may be use-cases "
"where you need to add additional resources to your chart’s fleet so that it "
"can better fit your environment. For information on how to enhance your "
"Fleet directory, see <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-"
"content\">Git Repository Contents</link>."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">(任意)</emphasis> 環境に合わせて、チャートのFleetに"
"リソースを追加しなければならないユースケースがあります。Fleetディレクトリを拡"
"張する方法については、「<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-"
"content\">Git Repository Contents (Gitリポジトリのコンテンツ)</link>」を参照"
"してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2225 l10n/source/edge.xml:2722
msgid ""
"In some cases, the default timeout Fleet uses for Helm operations may be "
"insufficient, resulting in the following error:"
msgstr ""
"場合によっては、Fleet がHelm操作に使用するデフォルトのタイムアウトが不十分で"
"、次のエラーが発生する可能性があります。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2226 l10n/source/edge.xml:2723
msgid ""
"In such cases, add the <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/ref-"
"crds#helmoptions\">timeoutSeconds</link> property under the <literal>helm</"
"literal> configuration of your <literal>fleet.yaml</literal> file."
msgstr ""
"このような場合は、<literal>fleet.yaml</literal>ファイルの<literal>helm</"
"literal>設定の下に、<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/ref-"
"crds#helmoptions\">timeoutSeconds</link>プロパティを追加してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2227 l10n/source/edge.xml:2724
msgid ""
"An <emphasis role=\"strong\">example</emphasis> for the <literal>longhorn</"
"literal> helm chart would look like:"
msgstr ""
"<literal>longhorn</literal> Helmチャートの<emphasis role=\"strong\">例</"
"emphasis>は次のようになります。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2228 l10n/source/edge.xml:2725
msgid "User Git repository structure:"
msgstr "ユーザGitリポジトリ構造:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2229 l10n/source/edge.xml:2726
msgid ""
"<literal>fleet.yaml</literal> content populated with user <literal>Longhorn</"
"literal> data:"
msgstr ""
"ユーザの<literal>Longhorn</literal>データが入力された<literal>fleet.yaml</"
"literal>の内容:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2230 l10n/source/edge.xml:2727
msgid ""
"These are just example values that are used to illustrate custom "
"configurations over the <literal>longhorn</literal> chart. They should "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">NOT</emphasis> be treated as deployment guidelines "
"for the <literal>longhorn</literal> chart."
msgstr ""
"これらは値の例であり、<literal>longhorn</literal>チャートのカスタム設定を示す"
"ために使用しているだけです。<literal>longhorn</literal>チャートの"
"デプロイメントのガイドラインと<emphasis role=\"strong\">みなさない</emphasis>"
"でください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2231 l10n/source/edge.xml:2728
msgid "Deploy the fleet for your chart"
msgstr "チャートのFleetのデプロイ"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2232
msgid ""
"You can deploy the fleet for your chart by either using a GitRepo (<xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-cluster-deploy-"
"gitrepo\"/>) or Bundle (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-"
"procedure-new-cluster-deploy-bundle\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"チャートのFleetをデプロイするには、GitRepo (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-"
"fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-cluster-deploy-gitrepo\"/>)またはバンドル"
"(<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-new-cluster-"
"deploy-bundle\"/>)のいずれかを使用できます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2233 l10n/source/edge.xml:2730
msgid ""
"While deploying your Fleet, if you get a <literal>Modified</literal> "
"message, make sure to add a corresponding <literal>comparePatches</literal> "
"entry to the Fleet’s <literal>diff</literal> section. For more information, "
"see <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-diffs\">Generating Diffs "
"to Ignore Modified GitRepos</link>."
msgstr ""
"Fleetをデプロイする場合に、<literal>Modified</literal>メッセージを取得した場"
"合、Fleetの<literal>diff</literal>セクションに対応する<literal>"
"comparePatches</literal>エントリを追加してください。詳細については、「<link "
"xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-diffs\">Generating Diffs to Ignore "
"Modified GitRepos (変更されたGitReposを無視する差分を生成する)</link> 」を参"
"照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2235 l10n/source/edge.xml:2732
msgid ""
"Fleet’s <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/ref-gitrepo\">GitRepo</"
"link> resource holds information on how to access your chart’s Fleet "
"resources and to which clusters it needs to apply those resources."
msgstr ""
"Fleetの<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/ref-gitrepo\">GitRepo</link>"
"リソースは、チャートのFleetリソースへのアクセス方法、それらのリソースを適用す"
"るのに必要なクラスタに関する情報を保持しています。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2236 l10n/source/edge.xml:2733
msgid ""
"The <literal>GitRepo</literal> resource can be deployed through the <link "
"xl:href=\"https://ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.13/integrations-in-"
"rancher/fleet/overview#accessing-fleet-in-the-rancher-ui\">Rancher UI</"
"link>, or manually, by <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/tut-"
"deployment\">deploying</link> the resource to the <literal>management "
"cluster</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>GitRepo</literal>リソースは、 <link xl:href=\"https://"
"ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.13/integrations-in-rancher/fleet/"
"overview#accessing-fleet-in-the-rancher-ui\">Rancher UI</link>を通じて、また"
"は手動で<literal>管理クラスタ</literal>にリソースを<link xl:href=\"https://"
"fleet.rancher.io/tut-deployment\">デプロイ</link>することで、デプロイできます"
"。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2237 l10n/source/edge.xml:2734
msgid ""
"Example <emphasis role=\"strong\">Longhorn</emphasis> <literal>GitRepo</"
"literal> resource for <emphasis role=\"strong\">manual</emphasis> deployment:"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">手動</emphasis>デプロイメントの<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Longhorn</emphasis> <literal>GitRepo</literal>リソースの例:"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2239 l10n/source/edge.xml:2736
msgid ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add\">Bundle</link> "
"resources hold the raw Kubernetes resources that need to be deployed by "
"Fleet. Normally it is encouraged to use the <literal>GitRepo</literal> "
"approach, but for use-cases where the environment is air-gapped and cannot "
"support a local Git server, <literal>Bundles</literal> can help you in "
"propagating your Helm chart Fleet to your target clusters."
msgstr ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add\">バンドル</link>リソース"
"は、Fleetによってデプロイされる必要がある生のKubernetesリソースを保持していま"
"す。通常、<literal>GitRepo</literal>アプローチを使用することを推奨されますが"
"、 環境がエアギャップされ、ローカルGitサーバをサポートできないユースケース用"
"に、<literal>バンドル</literal>がHelmチャートFleetをターゲットクラスタに伝播"
"するのに役立ちます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2240 l10n/source/edge.xml:2737
msgid ""
"A <literal>Bundle</literal> can be deployed either through the Rancher UI "
"(<literal>Continuous Delivery → Advanced → Bundles → Create from YAML</"
"literal>) or by manually deploying the <literal>Bundle</literal> resource in "
"the correct Fleet namespace. For information about Fleet namespaces, see the "
"upstream <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/namespaces#gitrepos-"
"bundles-clusters-clustergroups\">documentation</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>バンドル</literal>は、Rancher UI (<literal>［Continuous Delivery (継"
"続的デリバリ)］ → ［Advanced (詳細) ］→ ［Bundles (バンドル)］ → ［Create "
"from YAML (YALMから作成)］</literal>)を介して、または<literal>バンドル</"
"literal>リソースを正しいFleetネームスペースに手動でデプロイして、デプロイでき"
"ます。Fleetネームスペースについては、アップストリーム<link xl:href=\"https://"
"fleet.rancher.io/namespaces#gitrepos-bundles-clusters-clustergroups\">"
"ドキュメント</link>を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2241 l10n/source/edge.xml:2738
msgid ""
"<literal>Bundles</literal> for Edge Helm charts can be created by utilizing "
"Fleet’s <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add#convert-a-helm-"
"chart-into-a-bundle\">Convert a Helm Chart into a Bundle</link> approach."
msgstr ""
"Edge Helmチャートの<literal>バンドル</literal>は、Fleetの 「<link "
"xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add#convert-a-helm-chart-into-a-"
"bundle\">Convert a Helm Chart into a Bundle (Helmチャートをバンドルに変換す"
"る)</link>」 アプローチを利用して作成できます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2242 l10n/source/edge.xml:2739
msgid ""
"Below you can find an example on how to create a <literal>Bundle</literal> "
"resource from the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-"
"examples/blob/release-3.5.0/fleets/day2/chart-templates/longhorn/longhorn/"
"fleet.yaml\">longhorn</link> and <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-"
"edge/fleet-examples/blob/release-3.5.0/fleets/day2/chart-templates/longhorn/"
"longhorn-crd/fleet.yaml\">longhorn-crd</link> Helm chart fleet templates and "
"manually deploy this bundle to your <literal>management cluster</literal>."
msgstr ""
"以下に、<literal>バンドル</literal>リソースを<link xl:href=\"https://"
"github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/blob/release-3.5.0/fleets/day2/chart-"
"templates/longhorn/longhorn/fleet.yaml\">longhorn</link>と<link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/blob/release-3.5.0/"
"fleets/day2/chart-templates/longhorn/longhorn-crd/fleet.yaml\">longhorn-crd</"
"link> HelmチャートFleetテンプレートから作成し、このバンドルを<literal>管理"
"クラスタ</literal>に手動でデプロイする方法の例を示します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2243 l10n/source/edge.xml:2740
msgid ""
"To illustrate the workflow, the below example uses the <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples\">suse-edge/fleet-"
"examples</link> directory structure."
msgstr ""
"ワークフローを説明するため、以下の例では<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/"
"suse-edge/fleet-examples\">suse-edge/fleet-examples</link>ディレクトリ構造を"
"使用しています。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2244 l10n/source/edge.xml:2741
msgid ""
"Navigate to the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/"
"blob/release-3.5.0/fleets/day2/chart-templates/longhorn/longhorn/"
"fleet.yaml\">longhorn</link> Chart fleet template:"
msgstr ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/blob/release-"
"3.5.0/fleets/day2/chart-templates/longhorn/longhorn/fleet.yaml\">longhorn</"
"link>チャートFleetテンプレートに移動します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2245 l10n/source/edge.xml:2252
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2742 l10n/source/edge.xml:2748
msgid ""
"Create a <literal>targets.yaml</literal> file that will instruct Fleet to "
"which clusters it should deploy the Helm chart:"
msgstr ""
"FleetにHelmチャートのデプロイ先クラスタを指示する<literal>targets.yaml</"
"literal>ファイルを作成します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2246
msgid ""
"There are some use-cases where your local cluster could have a different "
"name."
msgstr "ローカルクラスタの名前が異なる場合があるユースケースがいくつかあります。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2247
msgid "To retrieve your local cluster name, execute the command below:"
msgstr "ローカルクラスタ名を取得するには、次のコマンドを実行します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2248 l10n/source/edge.xml:2744
msgid ""
"Convert the <literal>Longhorn</literal> Helm chart Fleet to a Bundle "
"resource using the <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/cli/fleet-cli/"
"fleet\">fleet-cli</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/cli/fleet-cli/fleet\">fleet-cli</"
"link>を使用して、<literal>Longhorn</literal> HelmチャートFleetを"
"バンドルリソースに変換します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2249 l10n/source/edge.xml:2745
msgid ""
"Fleet’s CLI can be retrieved from their <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/"
"rancher/fleet/releases/tag/v0.14.1\">release</link> <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Assets</emphasis> page (<literal>fleet-linux-amd64</"
"literal>)."
msgstr ""
"FleetのCLI は、<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/fleet/releases/tag/"
"v0.14.1\">リリース</link><emphasis role=\"strong\">アセット</emphasis>ページ"
"から取得できます(<literal>fleet-linux-amd64</literal>)。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2251 l10n/source/edge.xml:2747
msgid ""
"Navigate to the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/"
"blob/release-3.5.0/fleets/day2/chart-templates/longhorn/longhorn-crd/"
"fleet.yaml\">longhorn-crd</link> Chart fleet template:"
msgstr ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/blob/release-"
"3.5.0/fleets/day2/chart-templates/longhorn/longhorn-crd/fleet.yaml\">"
"longhorn-crd</link>チャートFleetテンプレートに移動します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2253 l10n/source/edge.xml:2749
msgid ""
"Convert the <literal>Longhorn CRD</literal> Helm chart Fleet to a Bundle "
"resource using the <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/cli/fleet-cli/"
"fleet\">fleet-cli</link>."
msgstr ""
"<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/cli/fleet-cli/fleet\">fleet-cli</"
"link>を使用して、<literal>Longhorn CRD</literal> HelmチャートFleetを"
"バンドルリソースに変換します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2254 l10n/source/edge.xml:2750
msgid ""
"Deploy the <literal>longhorn-bundle.yaml</literal> and <literal>longhorn-crd-"
"bundle.yaml</literal> files to your <literal>management cluster</literal>:"
msgstr ""
"<literal>longhorn-bundle.yaml</literal>と<literal>longhorn-crd-bundle.yaml</"
"literal>ファイルを<literal>管理クラスタ</literal>にデプロイします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2255
msgid ""
"Following these steps will ensure that <literal>SUSE Storage</literal> is "
"deployed on all of the specified management cluster."
msgstr ""
"これらの手順に従うと、<literal>SUSE Storage</literal>が指定された管理クラスタ"
"のすべてにデプロイされます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2256 l10n/source/edge.xml:2752
msgid "Manage the deployed Helm chart"
msgstr "デプロイされたHelmチャートの管理"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2257
msgid ""
"Once deployed with Fleet, for Helm chart upgrades, see <xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-fleet-managed-chart\"/"
">."
msgstr ""
"Fleetでデプロイした後のHelmチャートのアップグレードについては、<xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-fleet-managed-"
"chart\"/>を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2258 l10n/source/edge.xml:2754
msgid "I would like to upgrade a Fleet managed Helm chart"
msgstr "Fleetで管理されているHelmチャートをアップグレードしたい場合"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2259 l10n/source/edge.xml:2755
msgid ""
"Determine the version to which you need to upgrade your chart so that it is "
"compatible with the desired Edge release. Helm chart version per Edge "
"release can be viewed from the release notes (<xref linkend=\"release-"
"notes\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"目的のEdgeリリースと互換性を持つように、チャートをアップブレードする必要があ"
"るバージョンを決定します。EdgeリリースごとのHelmチャートバージョンは"
"リリースノート(<xref linkend=\"release-notes\"/>)から表示できます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2260 l10n/source/edge.xml:2756
msgid ""
"In your Fleet monitored Git repository, edit the Helm chart’s "
"<literal>fleet.yaml</literal> file with the correct chart <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">version</emphasis> and <emphasis role=\"strong\">repository</"
"emphasis> from the release notes (<xref linkend=\"release-notes\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"Fleetで監視されているGitリポジトリで、Helmチャートの<literal>fleet.yaml</"
"literal>ファイルを、リリースノート(<xref linkend=\"release-notes\"/>)から取得"
"した正しいチャートの<emphasis role=\"strong\">バージョン</emphasis>"
"と<emphasis role=\"strong\">リポジトリ</emphasis>で編集します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2261 l10n/source/edge.xml:2757
msgid ""
"After committing and pushing the changes to your repository, this will "
"trigger an upgrade of the desired Helm chart"
msgstr ""
"変更をコミットしてリポジトリにプッシュした後で、目的のHelmチャートの"
"アップグレードがトリガされます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2262 l10n/source/edge.xml:2758
msgid "I would like to upgrade a Helm chart deployed via EIB"
msgstr "EIBを介してデプロイされたHelmチャートをアップグレードしたい"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2263 l10n/source/edge.xml:2759
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"components-eib\"/> deploys Helm charts by creating a "
"<literal>HelmChart</literal> resource and utilizing the <literal>helm-"
"controller</literal> introduced by the <link xl:href=\"https://docs.rke2.io/"
"helm\">RKE2</link>/<link xl:href=\"https://docs.k3s.io/helm\">K3s</link> "
"Helm integration feature."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"components-eib\"/>は、<literal>HelmChart</literal>リソースを"
"作成し、<link xl:href=\"https://docs.rke2.io/helm\">RKE2</link>/<link "
"xl:href=\"https://docs.k3s.io/helm\">K3s</link> Helm統合機能によって導入され"
"た<literal>helm-controller</literal>を利用して、Helmチャートをデプロイします"
"。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2264 l10n/source/edge.xml:2760
msgid ""
"To ensure that a Helm chart deployed via <literal>EIB</literal> is "
"successfully upgraded, users need to do an upgrade over the respective "
"<literal>HelmChart</literal> resources."
msgstr ""
"<literal>EIB</literal>を介してデプロイされたHelmチャートが正常に"
"アップグレードされるようにするには、ユーザは各<literal>HelmChart</literal>"
"リソースに対してアップグレードを実行する必要があります。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2265 l10n/source/edge.xml:2761
msgid "Below you can find information on:"
msgstr "以下に関する情報が提供されています。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2266
msgid ""
"The general overview (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-"
"procedure-eib-deployed-chart-overview\"/>) of the upgrade process."
msgstr ""
"アップグレードプロセスの一般的な概要(<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-"
"helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-overview\"/>)。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2267
msgid ""
"The necessary upgrade steps (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-"
"upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-upgrade-steps\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"必要なアップグレード手順(<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-"
"procedure-eib-deployed-chart-upgrade-steps\"/>)。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2268
msgid ""
"An example (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-"
"deployed-chart-upgrade-example\"/>) showcasing a <link xl:href=\"https://"
"longhorn.io\">Longhorn</link> chart upgrade using the explained method."
msgstr ""
"説明した方法を使用した<link xl:href=\"https://longhorn.io\">Longhorn</link>"
"チャートアップグレードを示す例(<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-"
"upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-upgrade-example\"/>)。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2269
msgid ""
"How to use the upgrade process with a different GitOps tool (<xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-"
"upgrade-third-party\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"異なるGitOpsツールを使用したアップグレードプロセスを使用する方法(<xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-"
"upgrade-third-party\"/>)。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2271 l10n/source/edge.xml:2767
msgid ""
"Helm charts that are deployed via <literal>EIB</literal> are upgraded "
"through a <literal>fleet</literal> called <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/"
"suse-edge/fleet-examples/tree/release-3.5.0/fleets/day2/eib-charts-"
"upgrader\">eib-charts-upgrader</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>EIB</literal>を介してデプロイされたHelmチャートは、<link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/tree/release-3.5.0/"
"fleets/day2/eib-charts-upgrader\">eib-charts-upgrader</link>と呼ばれ"
"る<literal>フリート</literal>を通じてアップグレードされます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2272 l10n/source/edge.xml:2768
msgid ""
"This <literal>fleet</literal> processes <emphasis role=\"strong\">user-"
"provided</emphasis> data to <emphasis role=\"strong\">update</emphasis> a "
"specific set of HelmChart resources."
msgstr ""
"この<literal>フリート</literal>は、<emphasis role=\"strong\">ユーザが提供し"
"た</emphasis>データを処理し、特定のHelmChartリソースセットを<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">更新</emphasis>します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2273 l10n/source/edge.xml:2769
msgid ""
"Updating these resources triggers the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/k3s-"
"io/helm-controller\">helm-controller</link>, which <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">upgrades</emphasis> the Helm charts associated with the "
"modified <literal>HelmChart</literal> resources."
msgstr ""
"これらのリソースを更新すると、 <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/k3s-io/"
"helm-controller\">helm-controller</link>がトリガされ、変更された<literal>"
"HelmChart</literal>リソースに関連付けられているHelmチャートが<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">アップグレード</emphasis>されます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2274 l10n/source/edge.xml:2770
msgid "The user is only expected to:"
msgstr "ユーザは以下を行うことのみ求められます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2275 l10n/source/edge.xml:2771
msgid ""
"Locally <link xl:href=\"https://helm.sh/docs/helm/helm_pull/\">pull</link> "
"the archives for each Helm chart that needs to be upgraded."
msgstr ""
"アップグレードが必要な各Helmチャートのアーカイブをローカルで<link "
"xl:href=\"https://helm.sh/docs/helm/helm_pull/\">プル</link>します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2276 l10n/source/edge.xml:2772
msgid ""
"Pass these archives to the <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/"
"fleet-examples/blob/release-3.5.0/scripts/day2/generate-chart-upgrade-"
"data.sh\">generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</link> <literal>generate-chart-"
"upgrade-data.sh</literal> script, which will include the data from these "
"archives to the <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> fleet."
msgstr ""
"これらのアーカイブを<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-"
"examples/blob/release-3.5.0/scripts/day2/generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh\">"
"generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</link> <literal>generate-chart-upgrade-"
"data.sh</literal>スクリプトに渡します。これにより、これらのアーカイブのデータ"
"が <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal>フリートに含められます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2277 l10n/source/edge.xml:2773
msgid ""
"Deploy the <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> fleet to their "
"<literal>management cluster</literal>. This is done through either a "
"<literal>GitRepo</literal> or <literal>Bundle</literal> resource."
msgstr ""
"<literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleetを<literal>管理クラスタ</literal>"
"にデプロイします。これは<literal>GitRepo</literal>リソースまたは<literal>"
"バンドル</literal>リソースのいずれか通じて実行されます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2278
msgid ""
"Once deployed, the <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal>, with the help of "
"Fleet, will ship its resources to the desired management cluster."
msgstr ""
"デプロイされたら、<literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal>がFleetのサポートによ"
"って、そのリソースを目的の管理クラスタに配布します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2279 l10n/source/edge.xml:2775
msgid "These resources include:"
msgstr "これらのリソースには、次のものが含まれます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2280 l10n/source/edge.xml:2776
msgid ""
"A set of <literal>Secrets</literal> holding the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">user-provided</emphasis> Helm chart data."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">ユーザが提供する</emphasis>Helmチャートデータを保持"
"する<literal>Secret</literal>のセット。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2281 l10n/source/edge.xml:2777
msgid ""
"A <literal>Kubernetes Job</literal> which will deploy a <literal>Pod</"
"literal> that will mount the previously mentioned <literal>Secrets</literal> "
"and based on them <link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/"
"kubectl/generated/kubectl_patch/\">patch</link> the corresponding HelmChart "
"resources."
msgstr ""
"前述の<literal>Secret</literal>をマウントし、それらに基づいて対応する"
"HelmChartリソースに<link xl:href=\"https://kubernetes.io/docs/reference/"
"kubectl/generated/kubectl_patch/\">パッチを適用する</link> <literal>Pod</"
"literal>をデプロイする<literal>Kubernetes Job</literal>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2282 l10n/source/edge.xml:2778
msgid ""
"As mentioned previously this will trigger the <literal>helm-controller</"
"literal> which will perform the actual Helm chart upgrade."
msgstr ""
"前述のとおり、これにより、<literal>helm-controller</literal>がトリガされ、実"
"際の Helmチャートアップグレードが実行されます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2284
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-day2-management-helm-eib-"
"upgrade.png\" width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"
msgstr ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-day2-management-helm-eib-"
"upgrade.png\" width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><informalfigure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2285
msgid "fleet day2 management helm eib upgrade"
msgstr "fleet day2管理helm eibアップグレード"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2286 l10n/source/edge.xml:2782
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4360
msgid "Upgrade Steps"
msgstr "アップグレード手順"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2287 l10n/source/edge.xml:2783
msgid ""
"Clone the <literal>suse-edge/fleet-examples</literal> repository from the "
"correct release <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/"
"releases/tag/release-3.5.0\">tag</link>."
msgstr ""
"正しいリリース<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/"
"releases/tag/release-3.5.0\">タグ</link>から<literal>suse-edge/fleet-"
"examples</literal>リポジトリのクローンを作成します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2288 l10n/source/edge.xml:2784
msgid ""
"Create a directory in which you will store the pulled Helm chart archive(s)."
msgstr "取得したHelmチャートアーカイブを保存するディレクトリを作成します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2289 l10n/source/edge.xml:2785
msgid ""
"Inside of the newly created archive directory, <link xl:href=\"https://"
"helm.sh/docs/helm/helm_pull/\">pull</link> the archive(s) for the Helm "
"chart(s) you wish to upgrade:"
msgstr ""
"新規に作成されたアーカイブディレクトリ内で、アップグレードするHelmチャートの"
"アーカイブを<link xl:href=\"https://helm.sh/docs/helm/helm_pull/\">プル</"
"link>します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2290 l10n/source/edge.xml:2786
msgid ""
"From <emphasis role=\"strong\">Assets</emphasis> of the desired <link "
"xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/releases/tag/"
"release-3.5.0\">release tag</link>, download the <literal>generate-chart-"
"upgrade-data.sh</literal> script."
msgstr ""
"目的の<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/releases/"
"tag/release-3.5.0\">リリースタグ</link>の<emphasis role=\"strong\">アセット</"
"emphasis>から、<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal>スクリプトを"
"ダウンロードします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2291 l10n/source/edge.xml:2332
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2787 l10n/source/edge.xml:2827
msgid "Execute the <literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal> script:"
msgstr "<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal>スクリプトを実行します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2292 l10n/source/edge.xml:2788
msgid ""
"For each chart archive in the <literal>--archive-dir</literal> directory, "
"the script generates a <literal>Kubernetes Secret YAML</literal> file "
"containing the chart upgrade data and stores it in the <literal>base/"
"secrets</literal> directory of the fleet specified by <literal>--fleet-path</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>--archive-dir</literal>ディレクトリ内のチャートアーカイブごとに、"
"スクリプトにより、チャートアップグレードデータを含む<literal>Kubernetes "
"Secret YAML</literal>ファイルが生成され、<literal>--fleet-path</literal>によ"
"って指定されたフリートの<literal>base/secrets</literal>ディレクトリに保存され"
"ます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2293 l10n/source/edge.xml:2789
msgid ""
"The <literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal> script also applies "
"additional modifications to the fleet to ensure the generated "
"<literal>Kubernetes Secret YAML</literal> files are correctly utilized by "
"the workload deployed by the fleet."
msgstr ""
"<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal>スクリプトは、フリートに追加"
"の変更も適用し、生成された<literal>Kubernetes Secret YAML</literal>ファイルが"
"、フリートによってデプロイされたワークロードによって正しく利用されるようにし"
"ます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2294 l10n/source/edge.xml:2790
msgid ""
"Users should not make any changes over what the <literal>generate-chart-"
"upgrade-data.sh</literal> script generates."
msgstr ""
"ユーザは、<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal>スクリプトが生成す"
"る内容に変更を加えてはなりません。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2295 l10n/source/edge.xml:2791
msgid "The steps below depend on the environment that you are running:"
msgstr "以下の手順は、実行している環境によって異なります。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2296 l10n/source/edge.xml:2792
msgid ""
"For an environment that supports GitOps (e.g. is non air-gapped, or is air-"
"gapped, but allows for local Git server support):"
msgstr ""
"GitOpsをサポートする環境の場合(例: エアギャップされていない、エアギャップされ"
"たがローカルGitサーバサポートが可能):"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2297 l10n/source/edge.xml:2793
msgid ""
"Copy the <literal>fleets/day2/eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleet to the "
"repository that you will use for GitOps."
msgstr ""
"<literal>fleets/day2/eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleetを、GitOpsに使用する"
"リポジトリにコピーします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2298 l10n/source/edge.xml:2794
msgid ""
"Make sure that the Fleet includes the changes that have been made by the "
"<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal> script."
msgstr ""
"Fleetに<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal>スクリプトによって加"
"えられた変更が含まれていることを確認してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2299 l10n/source/edge.xml:2795
msgid ""
"Configure a <literal>GitRepo</literal> resource that will be used to ship "
"all the resources of the <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleet."
msgstr ""
"<literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleetのすべてのリソースを配布するため"
"に使用される<literal>GitRepo</literal>リソースを設定します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2300 l10n/source/edge.xml:2796
msgid ""
"For <literal>GitRepo</literal> configuration and deployment through the "
"Rancher UI, see <link xl:href=\"https://ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/"
"v2.13/integrations-in-rancher/fleet/overview#accessing-fleet-in-the-rancher-"
"ui\">Accessing Fleet in the Rancher UI</link>."
msgstr ""
"Rancher UIを通じた<literal>GitRepo</literal>の設定およびデプロイメントについ"
"ては、「<link xl:href=\"https://ranchermanager.docs.rancher.com/v2.13/"
"integrations-in-rancher/fleet/overview#accessing-fleet-in-the-rancher-ui\">"
"Accessing Fleet in the Rancher UI (Rancher UIでのFleetへのアクセス)</link>」"
"を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2301 l10n/source/edge.xml:2797
msgid ""
"For <literal>GitRepo</literal> manual configuration and deployment, see "
"<link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/tut-deployment\">Creating a "
"Deployment</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>GitRepo</literal>手動設定およびデプロイメントの場合、「<link "
"xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/tut-deployment\">Creating a Deployment "
"(デプロイメントの作成)</link>」を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2302 l10n/source/edge.xml:2798
msgid ""
"For an environment that does not support GitOps (e.g. is air-gapped and does "
"not allow local Git server usage):"
msgstr ""
"GitOpsをサポートしていない環境の場合 (例: エアギャップされ、ローカルGitサーバ"
"の使用が許可されていない):"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2303 l10n/source/edge.xml:2799
msgid ""
"Download the <literal>fleet-cli</literal> binary from the <literal>rancher/"
"fleet</literal> <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/fleet/releases/"
"tag/v0.14.1\">release</link> page (<literal>fleet-linux-amd64</literal> for "
"Linux). For Mac users, there is a Homebrew Formulae that can be used - <link "
"xl:href=\"https://formulae.brew.sh/formula/fleet-cli\">fleet-cli</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>rancher/fleet</literal> <link xl:href=\"https://github.com/rancher/"
"fleet/releases/tag/v0.14.1\">リリース</link>ページから<literal>fleet-cli</"
"literal>バイナリをダウンロードします(Linuxの場合は<literal>fleet-linux-"
"amd64</literal>)。Macユーザの場合、使用可能なHomebrew Formulaeがあります"
"(<link xl:href=\"https://formulae.brew.sh/formula/fleet-cli\">fleet-cli</"
"link>)。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2304 l10n/source/edge.xml:2800
msgid "Navigate to the <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleet:"
msgstr "<literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleetに移動します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2305 l10n/source/edge.xml:2801
msgid ""
"Create a <literal>targets.yaml</literal> file that will instruct Fleet where "
"to deploy your resources:"
msgstr ""
"リソースをデプロイする場所をFleetに指示する<literal>targets.yaml</literal>"
"ファイルを作成します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2308 l10n/source/edge.xml:2803
msgid ""
"Use the <literal>fleet-cli</literal> to convert the Fleet to a "
"<literal>Bundle</literal> resource:"
msgstr ""
"<literal>fleet-cli</literal>を使用して、Fleetを <literal>バンドル</literal>"
"リソースに変換します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2309 l10n/source/edge.xml:2804
msgid ""
"This will create a Bundle (<literal>bundle.yaml</literal>) that will hold "
"all the templated resource from the <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> "
"Fleet."
msgstr ""
"これにより、<literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleetからのすべての"
"テンプレート化されたリソースを保持するバンドル(<literal>bundle.yaml</"
"literal>)が作成されます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2310 l10n/source/edge.xml:2805
msgid ""
"For more information regarding the <literal>fleet apply</literal> command, "
"see <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/cli/fleet-cli/"
"fleet_apply\">fleet apply</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>fleet apply</literal>コマンドに関する詳細については、「<link "
"xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/cli/fleet-cli/fleet_apply\">fleet apply</"
"link>」を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2311 l10n/source/edge.xml:2806
msgid ""
"For more information regarding converting Fleets to Bundles, see <link "
"xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add#convert-a-helm-chart-into-a-"
"bundle\">Convert a Helm Chart into a Bundle</link>."
msgstr ""
"Fleetをバンドルに変換する方法に関する詳細については、「 <link "
"xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/bundle-add#convert-a-helm-chart-into-a-"
"bundle\">Convert a Helm Chart into a Bundle (Helmチャートのバンドルへの変換)"
"</link>」を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2312 l10n/source/edge.xml:2807
msgid ""
"Deploy the <literal>Bundle</literal>. This can be done in one of two ways:"
msgstr ""
"<literal>バンドル</literal>をデプロイします。これは次の2つの方法のいずれかで"
"実行できます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2313 l10n/source/edge.xml:2808
msgid ""
"Through Rancher’s UI - Navigate to <emphasis role=\"strong\">Continuous "
"Delivery → Advanced → Bundles → Create from YAML</emphasis> and either paste "
"the <literal>bundle.yaml</literal> contents, or click the <literal>Read from "
"File</literal> option and pass the file itself."
msgstr ""
"RancherのUIを通じて - <emphasis role=\"strong\">［Continuous Delivery (継続的"
"デリバリ)］→［Advanced (詳細)］→［Bundles (バンドル)］ → ［Create from YAML "
"(YAMLから作成)］</emphasis>に移動して、<literal>bundle.yaml</literal> "
"コンテンツを解析するか、［<literal>Read from File (ファイルから読み取り)</"
"literal>］オプションをクリックして、ファイル自体を渡します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2314 l10n/source/edge.xml:2809
msgid ""
"Manually - Deploy the <literal>bundle.yaml</literal> file manually inside of "
"your <literal>management cluster</literal>."
msgstr ""
"手動 - <literal>管理クラスタ</literal>内に<literal>bundle.yaml</literal>"
"ファイルを手動でデプロイします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2315
msgid ""
"Executing these steps will result in a successfully deployed "
"<literal>GitRepo/Bundle</literal> resource. The resource will be picked up "
"by Fleet and its contents will be deployed onto the target clusters that the "
"user has specified in the previous steps. For an overview of the process, "
"refer to <xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-"
"deployed-chart-overview\"/>."
msgstr ""
"これらの手順を実行すると、正常に<literal>GitRepo/バンドル</literal>リソースが"
"デプロイされます。リソースはFleetによって取得され、そのコンテンツはユーザが以"
"前の手順で指定したターゲットクラスタにデプロイされます。プロセスの概要につい"
"ては、<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-"
"deployed-chart-overview\"/>を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2316
msgid ""
"For information on how to track the upgrade process, you can refer to <xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-"
"upgrade-example\"/>."
msgstr ""
"アップグレードプロセスの追跡方法については、<xref linkend=\"management-day2-"
"fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-upgrade-example\"/>を参照して"
"ください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2317 l10n/source/edge.xml:2812
msgid ""
"Once the chart upgrade has been successfully verified, remove the "
"<literal>Bundle/GitRepo</literal> resource."
msgstr ""
"チャートアップグレードが正常に確認されたら、<literal>バンドル/GitRepo</"
"literal>リソースを削除します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2318
msgid ""
"This will remove the no longer necessary upgrade resources from your "
"<literal>management</literal> cluster, ensuring that no future version "
"clashes might occur."
msgstr ""
"これにより、<literal>管理</literal>クラスタから不要になった"
"アップグレードリソースが削除され、今後バージョンクラッシュが発生しないように"
"なります。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2319 l10n/source/edge.xml:2814
msgid "Example"
msgstr "例"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2320
msgid ""
"The example below demonstrates how to upgrade a Helm chart deployed via "
"<literal>EIB</literal> from one version to another on a <literal>management</"
"literal> cluster. Note that the versions used in this example are <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">not</emphasis> recommendations. For version recommendations "
"specific to an Edge release, refer to the release notes (<xref "
"linkend=\"release-notes\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"以下の例は、<literal>管理</literal>クラスタ上で、<literal>EIB</literal>を介し"
"てデプロイされたHelmチャートを、あるバージョンから別のバージョンに"
"アップグレードする方法を示しています。この例で使用されているバージョンは、推"
"奨バージョン<emphasis role=\"strong\">ではない</emphasis>ことに注意してくださ"
"い。Edgeリリースに固有のバージョン推奨事項については、リリースノート(<xref "
"linkend=\"release-notes\"/>)を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2321 l10n/source/edge.xml:2816
msgid "<emphasis>Use-case:</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>ユースケース:</emphasis>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2322
msgid ""
"A <literal>management</literal> cluster is running an older version of <link "
"xl:href=\"https://longhorn.io\">Longhorn</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>管理</literal>クラスタで、古いバージョンの<link xl:href=\"https://"
"longhorn.io\">Longhorn</link>が実行されています。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2323 l10n/source/edge.xml:2818
msgid ""
"The cluster has been deployed through EIB, using the following image "
"definition <emphasis>snippet</emphasis>:"
msgstr ""
"クラスタは、次のイメージ定義<emphasis>スニペット</emphasis>を使用して、EIBを"
"通じてデプロイされました。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2324 l10n/source/edge.xml:2819
msgid ""
"<literal>SUSE Storage</literal> needs to be upgraded to a version that is "
"compatible with the Edge 3.5 release. Meaning it needs to be upgraded to "
"<literal>1.10.1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>SUSE Storage</literal>は、Edge 3.5リリースと互換性のあるバージョンに"
"アップグレードする必要があります。つまり、<literal>1.10.1</literal>に"
"アップグレードする必要があります。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2325
msgid ""
"It is assumed that the <literal>management cluster</literal> is <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">air-gapped</emphasis>, without support for a local Git "
"server and has a working Rancher setup."
msgstr ""
"<literal>管理クラスタ</literal>がローカルGitサーバのサポートなしで<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">エアギャップ</emphasis>されており、Rancherセットアップが動作"
"していることを前提としています。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2326
msgid ""
"Follow the Upgrade Steps (<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-"
"procedure-eib-deployed-chart-upgrade-steps\"/>):"
msgstr ""
"アップグレード手順(<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-"
"procedure-eib-deployed-chart-upgrade-steps\"/>)に従います。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2327 l10n/source/edge.xml:2822
msgid ""
"Clone the <literal>suse-edge/fleet-example</literal> repository from the "
"<literal>release-3.5.0</literal> tag."
msgstr ""
"<literal>release-3.5.0</literal>タグから<literal>suse-edge/fleet-example</"
"literal>リポジトリのクローンを作成します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2328 l10n/source/edge.xml:2823
msgid ""
"Create a directory where the <literal>Longhorn</literal> upgrade archive "
"will be stored."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Longhorn</literal>アップグレードアーカイブが保存されるディレクトリを"
"作成します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2329 l10n/source/edge.xml:2824
msgid "Pull the desired <literal>Longhorn</literal> chart archive version:"
msgstr "目的の<literal>Longhorn</literal>チャートアーカイブバージョンを取得します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2330 l10n/source/edge.xml:2825
msgid ""
"Outside of the <literal>archives</literal> directory, download the "
"<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal> script from the "
"<literal>suse-edge/fleet-examples</literal> release <link xl:href=\"https://"
"github.com/suse-edge/fleet-examples/releases/tag/release-3.5.0\">tag</link>."
msgstr ""
"<literal>archives</literal>ディレクトリ以外で、<literal>suse-edge/fleet-"
"examples</literal>リリース<link xl:href=\"https://github.com/suse-edge/fleet-"
"examples/releases/tag/release-3.5.0\">タグ</link>から<literal>generate-chart-"
"upgrade-data.sh</literal>スクリプトをダウンロードします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2331 l10n/source/edge.xml:2826
msgid "Directory setup should look similar to:"
msgstr "ディレクトリセットアップは次のようになるはずです。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2333 l10n/source/edge.xml:2828
msgid ""
"The directory structure after the script execution should look similar to:"
msgstr "スクリプト実行後のディレクトリ構造は次のようになるはずです。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2334 l10n/source/edge.xml:2829
msgid "The files changed in git should look like this:"
msgstr "Gitで変更されたファイルは次のようになるはずです。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2335 l10n/source/edge.xml:2830
msgid ""
"Create a <literal>Bundle</literal> for the <literal>eib-charts-upgrader</"
"literal> Fleet:"
msgstr ""
"<literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleetの<literal>バンドル</literal>を作"
"成します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2336 l10n/source/edge.xml:2831
msgid "First, navigate to the Fleet itself:"
msgstr "まず、Fleet自体に移動します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2337 l10n/source/edge.xml:2832
msgid "Then create a <literal>targets.yaml</literal> file:"
msgstr "次に、<literal>targets.yaml</literal>ファイルを作成します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2338 l10n/source/edge.xml:2833
msgid ""
"Then use the <literal>fleet-cli</literal> binary to convert the Fleet to a "
"Bundle:"
msgstr ""
"次に、<literal>fleet-cli</literal>バイナリを使用して、Fleetをバンドルに変換し"
"ます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2339 l10n/source/edge.xml:2835
