msgstr "正常にデプロイされたら、バンドルは次のようになります。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><figure><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2348 l10n/source/edge.xml:2844
msgid "Successfully deployed Bundle"
msgstr "正常にデプロイされたバンドル"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><figure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2349 l10n/source/edge.xml:2845
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"day2_helm_chart_upgrade_example_2.png\" "
