msgstr ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"day2_helm_chart_upgrade_example_2.png\" "
"width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><figure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2350 l10n/source/edge.xml:2846
msgid "day2 helm chart upgrade example 2"
msgstr "day2 helmチャートアップグレード例2"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2352 l10n/source/edge.xml:2848
msgid ""
"After the successful deployment of the <literal>Bundle</literal>, to monitor "
"the upgrade process:"
msgstr ""
"<literal>バンドル</literal>のデプロイメントが成功した後で、"
"アップグレードプロセスを監視するには次のようにします。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2353 l10n/source/edge.xml:2849
msgid "Verify the logs of the <literal>Upgrade Pod</literal>:"
msgstr "<literal>アップグレードPod</literal>のログを確認します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2354
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"day2_helm_chart_upgrade_example_3_management.png\" width=\"100%\"/"
"> </imageobject>"
msgstr ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"day2_helm_chart_upgrade_example_3_management.png\" "
"width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><informalfigure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2355
msgid "day2 helm chart upgrade example 3 management"
msgstr "day2 helmチャートアップグレード例3管理"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2356 l10n/source/edge.xml:2852
msgid ""
"Now verify the logs of the Pod created for the upgrade by the helm-"
"controller:"
msgstr ""
"ここで、helm-controllerによってアップグレードに作成されたPodのログを確認しま"
"す。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2357 l10n/source/edge.xml:2853
msgid ""
"The Pod name will be with the following template - <literal>helm-install-"
"longhorn-&lt;random-suffix&gt;</literal>"
msgstr ""
"Pod名は次のテンプレートを使用します - <literal>helm-install-longhorn-"
"&lt;random-suffix&gt;</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2358 l10n/source/edge.xml:2854
msgid ""
"The Pod will be in the namespace where the <literal>HelmChart</literal> "
"resource was deployed. In our case this is <literal>kube-system</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Podは、<literal>HelmChart</literal>リソースがデプロイされたネームスペースにあ"
"ります。この場合、このネームスペースは<literal>kube-system</literal>です。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><figure><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2359 l10n/source/edge.xml:2855
msgid "Logs for successfully upgraded Longhorn chart"
msgstr "正常にアップグレードされたLonghornチャートのログ"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><figure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2360
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"day2_helm_chart_upgrade_example_4_management.png\" width=\"100%\"/"
"> </imageobject>"
msgstr ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"day2_helm_chart_upgrade_example_4_management.png\" "
"width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><figure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2361
msgid "day2 helm chart upgrade example 4 management"
msgstr "day2 helmチャートアップグレード例4管理"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2363 l10n/source/edge.xml:2859
msgid ""
"Verify that the <literal>HelmChart</literal> version has been updated by "
"navigating to Rancher’s <literal>HelmCharts</literal> section (<literal>More "
"Resources → HelmCharts</literal>). Select the namespace where the chart was "
"deployed, for this example it would be <literal>kube-system</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Rancherの<literal>HelmCharts</literal>セクション(<literal>［More Resources "
"(その他のリソース)］ → ［HelmCharts］</literal>)に移動して、<literal>"
"HelmChart</literal>のバージョンが更新されていることを確認します。チャートが"
"デプロイされたネームスペースを選択します。この例では、<literal>kube-system</"
"literal>です。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2364 l10n/source/edge.xml:2860
msgid "Finally check that the Longhorn Pods are running."
msgstr "最後に、 Longhorn Podが実行されていることを確認します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2365 l10n/source/edge.xml:2861
msgid ""
"After making the above validations, it is safe to assume that the Longhorn "
"Helm chart has been upgraded to the <literal>1.10.1</literal> version."
msgstr ""
"上記の検証後、Longhorn Helmチャートが<literal>1.10.1</literal>バージョンに"
"アップグレードされていると仮定しても問題ないでしょう。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2366 l10n/source/edge.xml:2862
msgid "Helm chart upgrade using a third-party GitOps tool"
msgstr "サードパーティのGitOpsツールを使用したHelmチャートのアップグレード"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2367 l10n/source/edge.xml:2863
msgid ""
"There might be use-cases where users would like to use this upgrade "
"procedure with a GitOps workflow other than Fleet (e.g. <literal>Flux</"
"literal>)."
msgstr ""
"ユーザがこのアップグレード手順をFleet以外のGitOpsワークフロー(<literal>Flux</"
"literal>など)で実行したいユースケースが存在する場合があります。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2368
msgid ""
"To produce the resources needed for the upgrade procedure, you can use the "
"<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal> script to populate the "
"<literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleet with the user provided data. "
"For more information on how to do this, see <xref linkend=\"management-day2-"
"fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-upgrade-steps\"/>."
msgstr ""
"アップグレード手順に必要なリソースを生成するには、 <literal>generate-chart-"
"upgrade-data.sh</literal>スクリプトを使用して、ユーザが提供するデータ"
"を<literal>eib-charts-upgrader</literal> Fleetに入力することができます。この"
"実行方法の詳細については、<xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-"
"procedure-eib-deployed-chart-upgrade-steps\"/>を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2369 l10n/source/edge.xml:2865
msgid ""
"After you have the full setup, you can use <link xl:href=\"https://"
"kustomize.io\">kustomize</link> to generate a full working solution that you "
"can deploy in your cluster:"
msgstr ""
"完全なセットアップ後、<link xl:href=\"https://kustomize.io\">kustomize</link>"
"を使用して、クラスタにデプロイ可能な完全な動作ソリューションを生成することが"
"できます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2370 l10n/source/edge.xml:2866
msgid ""
"If you want to include the solution to your GitOps workflow, you can remove "
"the <literal>fleet.yaml</literal> file and use what is left as a valid "
"<literal>Kustomize</literal> setup. Just do not forget to first run the "
"<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal> script, so that it can "
"populate the <literal>Kustomize</literal> setup with the data for the Helm "
"charts that you wish to upgrade to."
msgstr ""
"GitOpsワークフローにソリューションを含める場合は、<literal>fleet.yaml</"
"literal>ファイルを削除して、残ったものを有効な<literal>Kustomize</literal>"
"セットアップとして使用できます。まず、<literal>generate-chart-upgrade-"
"data.sh</literal>スクリプトを実行し、アップグレードするHelmチャートのデータ"
"を<literal>Kustomize</literal>セットアップに読み込ませることを忘れないでくだ"
"さい。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2371
msgid ""
"To understand how this workflow is intended to be used, it can be beneficial "
"to look at <xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-"
"deployed-chart-overview\"/> and <xref linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-"
"upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-upgrade-steps\"/>."
msgstr ""
"このワークフローの使用方法を理解するには、<xref linkend=\"management-day2-"
"fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-overview\"/>と<xref "
"linkend=\"management-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade-procedure-eib-deployed-chart-"
"upgrade-steps\"/>を参照すると役立つでしょう。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><title>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2372
msgid "Downstream clusters"
msgstr "ダウンストリームクラスタ"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2373
msgid ""
"The following steps do not apply to <literal>downstream</literal> clusters "
"managed by SUSE Telco Cloud (<xref linkend=\"atip\"/>). For guidance on "
"upgrading these clusters, refer to <xref linkend=\"atip-lifecycle-"
"downstream\"/>."
msgstr ""
"以下の手順は、SUSE Telco Cloud (<xref linkend=\"atip\"/>)によって管理され"
"る<literal>ダウンストリーム</literal>クラスタには適用されません。"
"ダウンストリームクラスタのアップグレードに関するガイダンスについては、<xref "
"linkend=\"atip-lifecycle-downstream\"/>を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2374
msgid ""
"This section covers the possible ways to perform \"Day 2\" operations for "
"different parts of your <literal>downstream</literal> cluster."
msgstr ""
"このセクションでは、 <literal>ダウンストリーム</literal>クラスタのさまざまな"
"部分に対して「Day 2」操作を実行可能な方法について説明します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2378
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-components\"/> - default components "
"used for all \"Day 2\" operations."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-components\"/> - すべての「Day 2」操作"
"に使用されるデフォルトコンポーネント。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2379
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-determine-use-case\"/> - provides an "
"overview of the Fleet custom resources that will be used and their "
"suitability for different \"Day 2\" operations use-cases."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-determine-use-case\"/> - 使用される"
"Fleetカスタムリソースの概要と、これらのリソースがさまざまな「Day 2」操作の"
"ユースケースに適しているかどうかを説明します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2380
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-upgrade-workflow\"/> - provides a workflow "
"guide for executing \"Day 2\" operations with Fleet."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-upgrade-workflow\"/> - Fleetを使用して「Day 2"
"」操作を実行するためのワークフローガイドを提供します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2381
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade\"/> - describes how to do "
"OS upgrades using Fleet."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade\"/> - Fleetを使用してOS"
"アップグレードを実行する方法を説明します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2382
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade\"/> - describes how to do "
"Kubernetes version upgrades using Fleet."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-k8s-upgrade\"/> - Fleetを使用して"
"Kubernetesバージョンアップグレードを実行する方法を説明します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2383
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade\"/> - describes how to do "
"Helm chart upgrades using Fleet."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade\"/> - Fleetを使用してHelm"
"チャートアップグレードを実行する方法を説明します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2385
msgid ""
"Below you can find a description of the default components that should be "
"set up on your <literal>downstream</literal> cluster so that you can "
"successfully perform \"Day 2\" operations using Fleet."
msgstr ""
"以下に、Fleetを使用して「Day 2」操作を正常に実行できるように、<literal>"
"ダウンストリーム</literal>クラスタで設定する必要がある"
"デフォルトコンポーネントについて説明します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2387
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Must</emphasis> be deployed on each downstream "
"cluster."
msgstr ""
"各ダウンストリームクラスタ上にデプロイする<emphasis role=\"strong\">必要があ"
"ります</emphasis>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2391
msgid ""
"For information on how to deploy <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis>, "
"first determine your use-case (<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-"
"determine-use-case\"/>) and then refer to System Upgrade Controller "
"installation - GitRepo (<xref linkend=\"components-system-upgrade-controller-"
"fleet-gitrepo\"/>), or System Upgrade Controller installation - Bundle "
"(<xref linkend=\"components-system-upgrade-controller-fleet-bundle\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis>をデプロイする方法については、まず"
"ユースケースを決定し(<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-determine-use-"
"case\"/>)、次に「System Upgrade Controllerのインストール - GitRepo」(<xref "
"linkend=\"components-system-upgrade-controller-fleet-gitrepo\"/>)、または「"
"System Upgrade Controller のインストール - バンドル」(<xref "
"linkend=\"components-system-upgrade-controller-fleet-bundle\"/>)を参照してく"
"ださい。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2404
msgid ""
"The following is a \"Day 2\" workflow that should be followed when upgrading "
"a downstream cluster to a specific Edge release."
msgstr ""
"以下に、ダウンストリームクラスタを特定のEdgeリリースにアップグレードする際に"
"従う必要のある「Day 2」ワークフローを示します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2405
msgid "OS upgrade (<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade\"/>)"
msgstr "OSアップグレード(<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade\"/>)"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2406
msgid ""
"Kubernetes version upgrade (<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-k8s-"
"upgrade\"/>)"
msgstr ""
"Kubernetesバージョンアップグレード(<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-k8s-"
"upgrade\"/>)"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2407
msgid ""
"Helm chart upgrade (<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-helm-upgrade\"/>)"
msgstr ""
"Helmチャートアップグレード(<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-helm-"
"upgrade\"/>)"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2411
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-components\"/> - additional "
"components used by the upgrade process."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-components\"/> - "
"アップグレードプロセスによって使用される追加のコンポーネント。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2412
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-overview\"/> - overview of "
"the upgrade process."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-overview\"/> - "
"アップグレードプロセスの概要。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2413
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-requirements\"/> - "
"requirements of the upgrade process."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-requirements\"/> - "
"アップグレードプロセスの要件。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2414
msgid ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-plan-deployment\"/> - "
"information on how to deploy <literal>SUC plans</literal>, responsible for "
"triggering the upgrade process."
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-plan-deployment\"/> - "
"アップグレードプロセスのトリガを担当する、<literal>SUC Plan</literal>を"
"デプロイする方法に関する情報。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2416
msgid ""
"This section covers the custom components that the <literal>OS upgrade</"
"literal> process uses over the default \"Day 2\" components (<xref "
"linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-components\"/>)."
msgstr ""
"このセクションでは、<literal>OSアップグレード</literal>プロセスがデフォルトの"
"「Day 2」コンポーネント(<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-components\"/>)"
"よりも使用するカスタムコンポーネントについて説明します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2424
msgid ""
"The services mentioned above are shipped on each node through a <literal>SUC "
"plan</literal> which must be located on the downstream cluster that is in "
"need of an OS upgrade."
msgstr ""
"上記サービスは、OSアップグレードが必要なダウンストリームクラスタ上に配置する"
"必要がある<literal>SUC Plan</literal>を通じて各ノードに配布されます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2426
msgid ""
"The upgrade of the operating system for downstream cluster nodes is done by "
"utilizing <literal>Fleet</literal> and the <literal>System Upgrade "
"Controller (SUC)</literal>."
msgstr ""
"ダウンストリームクラスタノードのオペレーティングシステムのアップグレードは"
"、<literal>Fleet</literal>と<literal>System Upgrade Controller (SUC)</"
"literal>を利用して実行されます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2430 l10n/source/edge.xml:2545
msgid ""
"<literal>GitRepo/Bundle</literal> resources are always deployed on the "
"<literal>management cluster</literal>. Whether to use a <literal>GitRepo</"
"literal> or <literal>Bundle</literal> resource depends on your use-case, "
"check <xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-determine-use-case\"/> for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"<literal>GitRepo/バンドル</literal>リソースは常に、<literal>管理クラスタ</"
"literal>上にデプロイされます。<literal>GitRepo</literal>リソースを使用する"
"か<literal>バンドル</literal>リソースを使用するかは、ユースケースによって異な"
"ります。詳細については、<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-determine-use-"
"case\"/>をご確認ください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2437
msgid ""
"The <literal>Kubernetes Job</literal> creates a systemd.service (<xref "
"linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-components-systemd-service\"/>) "
"for either package upgrade, or OS migration."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Kubernetes Job</literal>は、パッケージのアップグレードまたはOS"
"マイグレーションのためにsystemd.service (<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-"
"fleet-os-upgrade-components-systemd-service\"/>)を作成します。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><informalfigure><mediaobject>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2441
msgid ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-day2-downstream-os-upgrade.png\" "
"width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"
msgstr ""
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"fleet-day2-downstream-os-upgrade.png\" "
"width=\"100%\"/> </imageobject>"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><informalfigure><mediaobject><textobject><phrase>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2442
msgid "fleet day2 downstream os upgrade"
msgstr "fleet day2ダウンストリームosアップグレード"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2445
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">SCC registered machine</emphasis> - All downstream "
"cluster nodes should be registered to <literal><link xl:href=\"https://"
"scc.suse.com/\">https://scc.suse.com/</link></literal> which is needed so "
"that the respective <literal>systemd.service</literal> can successfully "
"connect to the desired RPM repository."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">SCC登録マシン</emphasis> - すべての"
"ダウンストリームクラスタノードを<literal><link xl:href=\"https://"
"scc.suse.com/\">https://scc.suse.com/</link></literal>に登録する必要がありま"
"す。これは、各<literal>systemd.service</literal>が目的のRPMリポジトリに正常に"
"接続できるようにするために必要です。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><important><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2457 l10n/source/edge.xml:2575
msgid ""
"<literal>Remove any previously deployed SUC Plans related to older Edge "
"release versions from the downstream cluster</literal> - can be done by "
"removing the desired cluster from the existing <literal>GitRepo/Bundle</"
"literal> <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-targets#target-"
"matching\">target configuration</link>, or removing the <literal>GitRepo/"
"Bundle</literal> resource altogether."
msgstr ""
"<literal>ダウンストリームクラスタから古いEdgeリリースバージョンに関連する以前"
"にデプロイしたSUC Planを削除する</literal> - これは、既存の<literal>GitRepo/"
"バンドル</literal><link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/gitrepo-"
"targets#target-matching\">ターゲット設定</link>から目的のクラスタを削除するか"
"、<literal>GitRepo/バンドル</literal>リソースを完全に削除することで、実行でき"
"ます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2460 l10n/source/edge.xml:2578
msgid ""
"If users attempt to upgrade, while there are existing <literal>SUC Plans</"
"literal> on the downstream cluster, they will see the following fleet error:"
msgstr ""
"ユーザがアップグレードを試す場合、ダウンストリームクラスタに既存の<literal>"
"SUC Plan</literal>がある場合は、次のフリートエラーが表示されます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2461
msgid ""
"As mentioned in <xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-overview\"/"
">, OS upgrades are done by shipping <literal>SUC plans</literal> to the "
"desired cluster through one of the following ways:"
msgstr ""
"<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-overview\"/>で説明したように"
"、OSアップグレードは、次の方法のいずれかの方法を使用して、<literal>SUC Plan</"
"literal>を目的のクラスタに配布することで実行されます。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2462
msgid ""
"Fleet <literal>GitRepo</literal> resource - <xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-"
"fleet-os-upgrade-plan-deployment-gitrepo\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Fleet <literal>GitRepo</literal>リソース - <xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-"
"fleet-os-upgrade-plan-deployment-gitrepo\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2463
msgid ""
"Fleet <literal>Bundle</literal> resource - <xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-"
"fleet-os-upgrade-plan-deployment-bundle\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Fleet <literal>バンドル</literal>リソース - <xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-"
"fleet-os-upgrade-plan-deployment-bundle\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2464 l10n/source/edge.xml:2582
msgid ""
"To determine which resource you should use, refer to <xref "
"linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-determine-use-case\"/>."
msgstr ""
"どのリソースを使用すべきかを判断するには、<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-"
"fleet-determine-use-case\"/>を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2465
msgid ""
"For use-cases where you wish to deploy the <literal>OS SUC plans</literal> "
"from a third-party GitOps tool, refer to <xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-"
"fleet-os-upgrade-plan-deployment-third-party\"/>"
msgstr ""
"<literal>OS SUC Plan </literal>をサードパーティのGitOpsツールからデプロイする"
"ユースケースの場合は、<xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-fleet-os-upgrade-plan-"
"deployment-third-party\"/>を参照してください。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2468
msgid ""
"Through the <literal>Rancher UI</literal> - <xref linkend=\"downstream-day2-"
"fleet-os-upgrade-plan-deployment-gitrepo-rancher\"/> (when <literal>Rancher</"
