#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2480 l10n/source/edge.xml:2602
msgid ""
"Edit the <emphasis role=\"strong\">GitRepo</emphasis> configuration, under "
"<literal>spec.targets</literal> specify your desired target list. By default "
"the <literal>GitRepo</literal> resources from the <literal>suse-edge/fleet-"
