"の他の特許または出願中の特許申請が含まれていることがありますが、これらに限定"
"されません。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:4383
msgid ""
"For SUSE trademarks, see the SUSE Trademark and Service Mark list (<link "
"xl:href=\"https://www.suse.com/company/legal/\">https://www.suse.com/company/"
"legal/</link>). All third-party trademarks are the property of their "
"respective owners. For SUSE brand information and usage requirements, please "
"see the guidelines published at <link xl:href=\"https://brand.suse.com/"
"\">https://brand.suse.com/</link>."
msgstr ""
"SUSEの商標については、SUSEの商標とサービスマークのリスト(<link "
"xl:href=\"https://www.suse.com/company/legal/\">https://www.suse.com/company/"
